{"type":null,"faqId":49814,"title":"游戏触摸位置不准确？","answer":"<div id=\"body46250162\">\n<p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264045__p66880658\"></p>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264045__p34639709145828\">玩游戏时手机触摸屏会点击偏位，可能是因为手机的虚拟按键被隐藏，在游戏中呼出虚拟按键即可恢复。</p>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264045__p3938477415034\">市面上的部分游戏是按照不隐藏导航栏设计的。进入游戏后隐藏导航栏时，画面会被拉伸，但画面坐标位置未做调整，故点击存在触摸位置偏差。</p>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264045__p65055018\">如果您需要在游戏中不显示导航栏，请先隐藏导航栏，再进入游戏。</p>\n<p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264045__p65055018\"></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"familylinks\"></div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264045","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615299000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":36,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"收音机，QQ音乐，同时使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}